<h2>Exploring the Results</h2>
<p>As soon as you arrive on the "Results" page, you'll be greeted with a home listings based on your selected filters or what home caught your interest. Each listing comes with a prominent image that gives you a quick glimpse of the property, inviting you to explore further.</p>

<ol>
    <li><strong>Link to Zillow:</strong> By clicking on the provided image or link, you'll be redirected to the Zillow page for the selected home. This seamless integration allows you to access additional details, high-resolution photos, and user reviews on one of the most popular real estate platforms.</li>
    <li><strong>Property Stats:</strong> Want to get the quick run down on the property without needing to click the link? It offers essential property statistics right on the Results page. You can easily find information on the price, property type, number of bedrooms and bathrooms, living size, and lot size. These details give you a comprehensive overview of the property, helping you determine if it aligns with your preferences and budget.</li>
</ol>

<h2>The Home Calculator</h2>
<p>One of the standout features is the built-in Home Calculator. You'll notice a calculator icon next to each listing price. Clicking on this icon allows you to automatically input the property details into the calculator. This feature is incredibly helpful when you want to assess your potential mortgage, monthly payments, how much you need to afford it, and other financial aspects of homeownership.</p>

<p>By streamlining the calculation process, it empowers you with the information you need to make informed decisions about your home purchase. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or a seasoned investor, this tool simplifies the complex financial aspects of real estate transactions.</p>

