<h2>Reroll and Filters</h2>
<p>We understans that your preferences may evolve during your home search journey. That's why the platform offers a "Reroll" option. With just a click, you can generate a new listing based on the same filters you've previously applied. This feature ensures that you're always presented with relevant listings that match your criteria.</p>

<p>But what if you're curious about the homes others have found? We have you covered there as well. You can explore listings generated by other users while still benefiting from their filter settings. This collaborative approach broadens your horizons and helps you discover homes you might have otherwise missed.</p>
